name: Dark Google Collection
description: Google but everything is dark and cleaned up a bit.
additional_info:
If something's missing feel free to comment or what have you, I'll update it as I go.

Release:
- Pree much all standard Google Search things. Search, Images, Games & Toys, Tools, Videos, Shopping, News, Books, Flights, have all at least been started.

Update 1:
- More work on Flights, Finance, and Personal
- MInor changes to already done sections for consistency

Update 2:
- Added most of Maps 
- Added Translate
- Upkeep
- Probably more I've forgotten

Update 3:
- Updated weather information thing
- Updated emergency information thing
- Updated Twitter previews
- Updated Image titles not showing

Update 4:
- Updated Dictionary results

Update 4.1:
- Updated Dictionary results properly

Update 4.2:
- Fixed changes Google did to a few things. 
- Learned that changing the Apps popup won't be possible for a while thanks to iframes, if you know how to get around that let me know!

Update 5:
- Updated Images to not have the annoying white parts at the top, thanks Google

Update 6:
- Google made the searchform global, so some stuff was broken that shouldn't have been. All fixed now.

Update 7:
- Updated some stuff on the main search page
- Updated some Flight page stuff
- Merged in my Dark Google Accounts CSS, so those should be covered by this as well to avoid needing to install them separately

Update 8 - The Google Play Update!
- Google Play, for the most part now, is dark!
- Updated the Other Google Services dropdown thing, that was an iframe so a little weird but now it's dark too!
- Updated some Search stuff that was missed

Update 9 
- Minor style changes/updates in search
- Product view when a product is searched now dark
- Another view on the side was made dark too

Update 10
- Made the Google Translate Extension view darker through a roundabout way

Update 11
- Updated Search Suggestion dropdown
- Updated Flights/Hotels/Etc pages
- Updated Shopping page 
- Updated Translate Page
- Fixed the Apps dropdown next to the profile picture

Update 12
- Google Fonts, now dark.
- Updated the Account Switcher window
- Updated the Upload/Select File window (not the Windows one, Google's Docs one)

Update 13
- Gmail!

Update 14
- Gmail updates (will slowly be improved over time with standard or common email background colours)
- Updated some Google Search Services things
- Updated the Define window

Update 15
- More Gmail updates
- Minor Search updates
- The Timer search app has been darkened

Update 16
- More Gmail Updates
- Minor Search updates
- Google Docs Suite in progress. Google Docs itself, along with Slides should be moreorless done.

Update 17
- More Gmail updates (these are gonna be common as I come across them)
- Minor Search updates
- Minor Google Docs changes
- Minor Translate changes
- Minor Support changes

Update 18
- Translate may have broken for some people, so I fixed it (this did not affect everyone)
- Minor improvements to the Google App dropdown

Update 19
- Updated Maps
- Updated Search
- Updated Accounts
- Updated News
- Updated Books
- Added Trends
- Added Patents
- Added Podcasts
- Added User Research
- Added Arts and Culture
- Probably missed some stuff, gonna purposely update less unless a major update is needed

Update 20: The "Well Then" Update
- Updated Search (This will likely be ongoing, Google's making changes all the time)
- Updated Maps
- Updated Accounts
- Updated Docs
- Updated Play
- Updated Books
- Updated News
- Updated Shopping
- Updated Flights (and other Travel ones)
- Added Pay
- Added Groups 
- Added Drive
- I definitely missed other stuff, but you get the idea.

Update 21: The "Just... Why?" Update
- Updated Search a bunch because of minor things that really did not need to be changed.
- Updated Docs
- Updated Drive
- Updated Support
- Updated Play

Update 22: The "Google Hates Me" Update
- Updated minor Search elements (seriously, they changed the colour of search results?)
- Updated Mail
- Updated Drive
- Minor updates here and there
- Added Admin 
- Added Workspace
- Added Calendar
